The best thing a woman can have is her shit together 🤎 I never wanted to depend on anyone for the things I wanted out of life. I always knew that I was going to be a woman who hustle to live a life luxury and anything anyone else brought to the table was just extra never a necessity. 

I always thought it was so dope to see a group of fine, healthy, and paid women together elevating the culture. 

Where y’all at? I want to connect with atleast 10 women this month. Dm me let’s work.

node.text:
I’m honored to announce that I will be a live speaker at The Awakening in Houston TX September 24-26th 🦋

Im excited to share my truth. One thing I know is that everybody is facing a battle that we know nothing about and to be so young I’ve had to fight a lot of mental battles and still everyday I fight. 

Many people have come to these events suicidal, depressed, and not knowing their self worth. However whatever you believe is right and you are who you say you are. Change the way you speak to yourself and your life will change.

Change happens with a decision, click the link in my bio and secure your seat at the awakening it’s only 36 seats left and it’s a must I see some of my followers in the building 🦋🙏🏾
